<item>
            <title>[CXF-6843] http 406 not acceptable should be returned if query parameter value can&apos;t be converted </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-6843</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For query parameter conversion exception, it  should return 406 http status in response.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
